FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1783653540
OL,3,CLabour MPs overwhelmingly back Andy
OL,4,CBurnham for party leadership
OL,6,FThe former Greater Manchester mayor
OL,7,Fsecured the nominations ` amounting to
OL,8,F80% of the parliamentary party ` by
OL,9,F5pm on Thursday, the first day MPs
OL,10,Fcould formally back a leadership
OL,11,Fcandidate.
OL,13,FEven before nominations opened, Mr
OL,14,FBurnham seemed almost certain to enjoy
OL,15,Fa coronation as Labour leader as the
OL,16,Fonly declared candidate in the race to
OL,17,Fsucceed Sir Keir.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
