CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1783653540
OL,3,CLabour MPs overwhelmingly back Andy
OL,4,CBurnham for party leadership
OL,6,FBut the size of his support in the
OL,7,Fparliamentary party means even a late
OL,8,Fchallenger now has virtually no hope
OL,9,Fof securing the required nominations.
OL,11,FMr Burnham said he was "deeply
OL,12,Fgrateful" to the 322 MPs who had
OL,13,Fbacked him, saying their support
OL,14,F"comes from across the PLP
OL,15,F(Parliamentary Labour Party) and
OL,16,Freflects a shared belief that Britain
OL,17,Fneeds a new approach to politics".
OL,26,@sD@XOUtD@IO]vD@AOUyD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1783653540
OL,3,CLabour MPs overwhelmingly back Andy
OL,4,CBurnham for party leadership
OL,6,FHe added: "I want to empower MPs to
OL,7,Fbring the experiences of their
OL,8,Fconstituents into the heart of
OL,9,Fgovernment and harness the full
OL,10,Fbreadth of our Labour movement,
OL,11,Fdrawing on all its traditions and
OL,12,Fbeliefs in pursuit of a common purpose.
OL,14,F"I want to thank every colleague who
OL,15,Fhas nominated me for their commitment
OL,16,Fto that vision."
OL,26,@nD@KOUvD@AOUxD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
