PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1783653540
OL,3,CLabour MPs overwhelmingly back Andy
OL,4,CBurnham for party leadership
OL,6,FAs nominations opened on Thursday, Sir
OL,7,FKeir told reporters he thought Mr
OL,8,FBurnham would make a good prime
OL,9,Fminister, saying they had known each
OL,10,Fother "a long time".
OL,12,FThe Prime Minister said he had worked
OL,13,Fclosely with Mr Burnham on the
OL,14,FInvestigatory Powers Bill when the
OL,15,Flatter was shadow home secretary in
OL,16,F2015, adding the legislation was
OL,17,F"really important in terms of the
OL,18,Fpowers and capabilities that our
OL,19,Fsecurity and intelligence services
OL,20,Fneed".
OL,26,@rD@GOUrD@SO]yD@AOU|D@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1783653540
OL,3,CLabour MPs overwhelmingly back Andy
OL,4,CBurnham for party leadership
OL,6,FHe also referred to their
OL,7,Fcollaboration since 2024 on Northern
OL,8,FPowerhouse Rail, which he said was "an
OL,9,Fexample of devolution at its best",
OL,10,Fand Mr Burnham's response to the
OL,11,Fattack on the Heaton Park synagogue
OL,12,Flast year.
OL,14,FSir Keir said: "Andy was the first
OL,15,Fperson I phoned to find out what was
OL,16,Fhappening, where things were at.
OL,18,F"When I went to Manchester, I spent
OL,19,Fthe whole time with him, with the
OL,20,Fcommunity and with others. So, I've
OL,21,Falways worked very well with Andy."
OL,26,@pD@dOUqD@bO]vD@POUzD@AOU}D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
