PN,30310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1783653540
OL,3,CLabour MPs overwhelmingly back Andy
OL,4,CBurnham for party leadership
OL,6,FAsked whether Mr Burnham would be a
OL,7,Fbetter prime minister than him, Sir
OL,8,FKeir replied laughing: "These are
OL,9,Fthings best judged by other people."
OL,11,FNominations remain officially open
OL,12,Funtil July 16 and, in the absence of
OL,13,Fany other candidates, Mr Burnham will
OL,14,Fbe formally declared Labour leader at
OL,15,Fa special conference on July 17 and is
OL,16,Fexpected to become prime minister on
OL,17,FJuly 20.
OL,26,@pD@XOUqD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
