OL,3,CLabour MPs overwhelmingly back Andy
OL,4,CBurnham for party leadership
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Mr Burnham set out more of
OL,7,Fhis vision for British foreign policy
OL,8,Fand signalled a tougher stance towards
OL,9,FIsrael over its military operations in
OL,10,FGaza.
OL,12,FIn a video on social media, he
OL,13,Fapologised for Labour's previous
OL,14,Fstance, saying his party "didn't get
OL,15,Fit right" and the UK had been "too
OL,16,Fslow to call for a ceasefire".
OL,26,@vD@ZOUwD@IO]wD@_OUxD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
