PN,30312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1783653540
OL,3,CLabour MPs overwhelmingly back Andy
OL,4,CBurnham for party leadership
OL,6,FMr Burnham suggested that his
OL,7,Fgovernment would "do more to
OL,8,Fstrengthen our approach", including
OL,9,F"looking at further sanctions, both on
OL,10,Fthose involved in the violence in
OL,11,FGaza, but also looking at measures to
OL,12,Fban trade in goods with illegal
OL,13,Fsettlements".
OL,26,@oD@ROUpD@XO]qD@AOUuD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
