OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1783653540
OL,3,CLabour MPs overwhelmingly back Andy
OL,4,CBurnham for party leadership
OL,6,FHis comments followed an article in
OL,7,FThe Times in which he said he would
OL,8,Fseek stability in foreign policy,
OL,9,Fsetting out his commitment to Nato,
OL,10,Fthe nuclear deterrent, maintaining
OL,11,Fclose ties with the US and support for
OL,12,FUkraine as well as closer relations
OL,13,Fwith the EU.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/13
